high_descs: Go to the table past the stove on the left.
Pick up the head of lettuce on the table.
Take the lettuce to the fridge.
Chill the head of lettuce in the fridge.
Turn and go to the counter to the left of the sink.
Set the cold lettuce down on the counter to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Set a cold head of lettuce on the counter by the toaster.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward a few steps, then turn right again to face the side of the white table.
Pick up the head of lettuce that is on the table.
Turn right to move around the table, walk past the table and up to the refrigerator.
Place the lettuce in the fridge to chill before taking it back out.
Turn to your right and walk over to the kitchen counter.
Place the head of lettuce in the corner of the countertop, to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Move a chilled head of lettuce to the countertop.

high_descs: Turn right and turn right again to face the white table with the head of lettuce on it.
Pick up the head of lettuce from the table.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the head of lettuce in the fridge on the second shelf, close the door and let the lettuce chill for a few seconds, take the lettuce out of the fridge, and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the head of lettuce down on the counter to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: To chill a head of lettuce and place on the counter next to the toaster.
